    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>Our first game is now available on Steam!</strong> 🔥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After <strong>6 years of development</strong>, from the first concept to the final release, we proudly present <strong>RazePact</strong> — a game made entirely in <strong>Construct 2</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>RazePact</strong> combines the best of classics like <strong>Mega Man X4 and X5</strong> with the fast-paced action of <strong>hack n’ slash</strong> combat and the nostalgic charm of games like <strong>Grand Chase</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll control <strong>Soul</strong>, a small wandering spirit searching for answers within a <strong>dark dungeon full of mysteries</strong>. With each battle, you grow stronger — and closer to uncovering the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕹️ Throughout this world, you’ll find <strong>various upgrades</strong> and <strong>unique altar mechanics</strong> that enhance your abilities as you progress.<br>Activate mechanisms, overcome challenges, and face <strong>epic boss battles</strong> that will truly test your skill and precision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 The fights are intense and challenging, but you’ll have <strong>well-placed checkpoints</strong> to bring you back close to where you fell — no need to replay entire stages or start over like in some roguelikes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ We hope you <strong>enjoy exploring this universe</strong> and don’t forget to <strong>leave a review on Steam</strong> to share your thoughts about the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br> <br> <br> </p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
